graph TB
    subgraph "Model Registry Operator"
        ControllerManager[Controller Manager]
        WebhookServer[Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        ControllerManager -->|validates/defaults| WebhookServer
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        ModelRegistryCR[ModelRegistry CR<br/>modelregistry.opendatahub.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    subgraph "Managed Resources (per ModelRegistry)"
        Deployment[Model Registry Deployment]
        Service[Model Registry Service<br/>8080/TCP REST, 9090/TCP gRPC]
        ServiceAccount[Service Account]
        Role[RBAC Role]

        subgraph "Optional Istio Resources"
            Gateway[Istio Gateway]
            VirtualService[VirtualService]
            DestinationRule[DestinationRule]
            AuthzPolicy[AuthorizationPolicy]
        end

        subgraph "Optional Authorino"
            AuthConfig[AuthConfig]
        end

        subgraph "Optional OpenShift"
            Route[OpenShift Route]
        end
    end

    subgraph "Model Registry Deployment Containers"
        RestContainer[REST Container<br/>8080/TCP<br/>model-registry]
        GrpcContainer[gRPC Container<br/>9090/TCP<br/>mlmd-grpc-server]
        RestContainer -->|localhost| GrpcContainer
    end

    User[User/Admin] -->|creates| ModelRegistryCR
    ModelRegistryCR -->|watched by| ControllerManager
    ControllerManager -->|reconciles| Deployment
    ControllerManager -->|creates| Service
    ControllerManager -->|creates| ServiceAccount
    ControllerManager -->|creates| Role
    ControllerManager -->|creates if Istio enabled| Gateway
    ControllerManager -->|creates if Istio enabled| VirtualService
    ControllerManager -->|creates if Istio enabled| DestinationRule
    ControllerManager -->|creates if Istio enabled| AuthzPolicy
    ControllerManager -->|creates if Istio enabled| AuthConfig
    ControllerManager -->|creates if route enabled| Route

    Deployment -->|contains| RestContainer
    Deployment -->|contains| GrpcContainer

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        PostgreSQL[(PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP)]
        MySQL[(MySQL<br/>3306/TCP)]
        IstioMesh[Istio Service Mesh]
        Authorino[Authorino]
    end

    GrpcContainer -->|stores metadata| PostgreSQL
    GrpcContainer -->|stores metadata| MySQL
    Service -->|routed via| IstioMesh
    AuthzPolicy -->|enforces via| Authorino
    Gateway -->|external access| IstioMesh

    subgraph "Integration Points"
        ODHOperator[ODH/RHOAI Operator]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API]
        Prometheus[Prometheus]
    end

    ODHOperator -->|installs| ControllerManager
    ControllerManager -->|manages resources| K8sAPI
    Prometheus -->|scrapes metrics| ControllerManager

    style ControllerManager fill:#4a90e2
    style WebhookServer fill:#4a90e2
    style ModelRegistryCR fill:#f5a623
    style RestContainer fill:#7ed321
    style GrpcContainer fill:#7ed321
    style PostgreSQL fill:#e8e8e8
    style MySQL fill:#e8e8e8
    style IstioMesh fill:#e8e8e8
    style Authorino fill:#e8e8e8
